data.description: This beautifully maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has multiple updates inside and out! Fresh paint throughout, laundry room addition, water softener (2017), water heater (2020), laminate flooring, new carpet, and new roof. The main level has a full bath, two bedrooms, living room with a beautiful bay window, dining room with access to the deck and large backyard with a raised garden and newly built custom shed. The master bedroom on the lower level includes his and her closets, a fully renovated primary bathroom with dual sinks, and walk-out patio. Downstairs is also home to a spacious family room, wired for surround sound, and a large laundry room with a built-in folding table. Recessed lighting and three-panel oak doors complete the lower layout. The three-car garage is insulated and heated with tons of cabinets and workspace. Just minutes from the interstate, this move-in ready property is just waiting for you to call it home! Call to schedule your private showing today!
